git vconfig          [<options>] - Add    version configuration options.
git vconfig --remove [<options>] - Remove version configuration options.

    -h|--help               display help

'update-version' section:

    --version-props[=FILE]  Use Version.props style files (default to './Version.props').
    --assembly-info[=FILE]  Use AssemblyInfo.cs style files (default to '*/AssemblyInfo*.cs').
    --csproj[=FILE]         Use .NET Framework C# project style files (default to '*/*.cspro').
    --custom                Add a custom version updater template file (update-version).
    
    example:
        git vconfig --version-props                     # update_version.version-props = ./Version.props
        git vconfig --version-props --remove            # remove 'update_version.version-props' key
        git vconfig --assembly-info='./AssemblyInfo.cs' # update_version.version-props = ./AssemblyInfo.cs
